STATE EX REL. JACKSON
v.
BRUSH. 2017-1670 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 28, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Mandamus and Prohibition. On relator's motion for leave to supplement complaint. Motion granted. On respondents' motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.
